Package it.polimi.ingsw.observer

Interface ViewObserver

All Known Implementing Classes:
ClientController
public interface ViewObserver
This class is related to the view part of the application. Depending on the observer turned on there are different methods to be called. Graphic Controller class (GUI) and CLI implements ViewObserver.
